h3. Summary

We would like to have the ability to add the images in the request form. For example, on radio buttons like below:

!Unbenannt.PNG|width=364,height=77!

h3. Issue Summary

When viewing issues in a queue, fields like Description or any other multi-line text fields display the entire content which makes it difficult to browse through the entire queue if these fields have a lot of data

 

We would like to have the ability to display these fields in the queue such that we show only X no of charaters and the rest can be "...". For example:

 
{code:java}
Example text...
{code}

As explained [here|https://support.atlassian.com/jira-service-desk-cloud/docs/add-an-organization-to-a-service-desk-project], 
{quote}
Both administrators and agents can add organizations to a service desk project.
{quote}
now customers can't create and edit organizations. Keeping track of and managing all of these organizations is very hard, and there is a need to provide a way for customers to manage them all themself (self-service).

